OL,11,G0100 Outback Truckers
OL,12,     FJeff Fulwood takes on one of the
OL,13,     Fmost notorious roads in Australia
OL,14,     Fto deliver a vital supply run to a
OL,15,     Fremote community; the only problem
OL,16,     F- it's missing an essential load.
